### Comparación URL encoding vs Text escaping
# URL encoding (método tradicional)
GET http://localhost:9090/api/v1/label/my%2Dlabel/values
GET http://localhost:9090/api/v1/label/label%2Ewith%2Edots/values

# Text escaping (método nuevo UTF-8)
GET http://localhost:9090/api/v1/label/my\x2dlabel/values
GET http://localhost:9090/api/v1/label/label\x2ewith\x2edots/values

### Casos complejos con filtros
GET http://localhost:9090/api/v1/label/my\x2dlabel/values?match[]=up&match[]=node_cpu_seconds_total